room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Mastermind Escape Games in Jacksonville

room_description: As your final test to become a part of a world-renowned crime syndicate, you have to rob the Jacksonville bank. Your boss will distract the guards and cops for an hour. The task is not just to escape, but to steal as much cash as possible.
